{"tid":2191635,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本補貼日企由中國搬遷至印度和孟加拉","createTime":"2020-09-06T14:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T01:27:25.000Z","uid":79563,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4d439d5c567718401336ea7f564f9713f9a89ce2","tid":2191635,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:41:25.000Z","msg":"&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 日本日前表示擴大日本公司搬遷補貼方案的範圍,新增印度和孟加拉國等國家,來幫助日本公司撤出中國。該計劃最初補貼日本工廠撤出中國、搬回日本或將產線轉移到東南亞。<br />\n<br />\n日本、印度和澳洲的貿易部長周二作出決定,開始在印度太平洋地區建立彈性的供應鏈。為了減少對中國的貿易依賴,這三個國家強調了建立自由、公平和可預測的貿易環境的必要性,並敦促亞太地區志趣相投的國家參加。 (BC)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/日本補貼日企由中國搬遷至印度和孟加拉-062142560.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%A3%9C%E8%B2%BC%E6%97%A5%E4%BC%81%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%90%AC%E9%81%B7%E8%87%B3%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%92%8C%E5%AD%9F%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%89-062142560.html&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4lLtzFpi4hzjoOYPfLz2gO4%3D&h=e721be2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/日本補貼日企由中國搬遷至印度和孟加拉-062142560.html</a>"},{"pid":"a1f8495aaff392853e6d3ae923c1241b71c7541f","tid":2191635,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"bed832d588a0853f38b59b632499030d76fbea71","tid":2191635,"uid":82394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:56:46.000Z","msg":"希望多啲廠搬遷<br />\n孟加拉好似都有1億人，有大量勞工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9550e508c9acfcc0c1b20db8bc0b8a18961fa782","tid":2191635,"uid":266294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"